    "description": "Are you a skilled Full Stack Developer looking for your next big career move? Sasken Technologies Holdings Services in Jabalpur offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Sasken Technologies Holdings Services:\nSasken Technologies Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in Go\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Sasken Technologies Holdings Services!",
